data.description: Brand New Metal Roof! Located in the heart of Vero Beach, this property offers easy access to the city's renowned cultural attractions, fine dining, and pristine beaches. Whether you're a year-round resident or seeking a seasonal escape, this oasis provides the quintessential Florida lifestyle. This charming fully furnished 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom, pool home with detached pool room. The outdoor space is perfect for entertaining with a focus on indoor-outdoor living.
